tc.research_name.PUREIRON=§7Metal Purification
tc.research_text.PUREIRON=§7Purification of metals into native clusters
tc.research_page.PUREIRON.1=§7Native clusters are rare concentrations of metals in its purest form. You have discovered a way to purify and concentrate normal iron ore into a native iron cluster.<BR>When smelted these clusters produces twice the normal amount of iron ingots.
#
tc.research_name.PUREGOLD=§7Gold Purification
tc.research_text.PUREGOLD=§7Purification of gold into native clusters
tc.research_page.PUREGOLD.1=§7Native clusters are rare concentrations of metals in its purest form. You have discovered a way to purify and concentrate normal gold ore into a native gold cluster.<BR>When smelted these clusters produces twice the normal amount of gold ingots.
#
tc.research_name.PURECOPPER=§7Copper Purification
tc.research_text.PURECOPPER=§7Purification of copper into native clusters
tc.research_page.PURECOPPER.1=§7Native clusters are rare concentrations of metals in its purest form. You have discovered a way to purify and concentrate normal copper ore into a native copper cluster.<BR>When smelted these clusters produces twice the normal amount of copper ingots.
#
